{"tid":1277474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想問琴日企希慎出面果個元朗區議員係邊撚個","createTime":"2019-07-02T07:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T16:40:32.000Z","uid":15660,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e75c05dd93bc3b6cd8e7a3d7a4b19083fb1b454d","tid":1277474,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"我係希慎一落去軒尼斯道<br />\n就聽到佢嗌咪<br />\n佢話而家係立法會衝緊既人係鬼<br />\n話琴日係元朗聽到d黑社會話有d後生仔話聽日會去衝<br />\n仲話有佢d朋友認得出衝緊既人係琴日有份撐警<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母臭閪呀<br />\n乜撚野都係聽人講聽人講<br />\n割蓆分化樣樣做齊<br />\n屌柒佢佢當聽唔撚到<br />\n<br />\n學似你地咁和理非係度叫下然後籌下錢<br />\n遊完行數下個籌款箱有幾錢然後去慶功<br />\n咁樣就最撚好？<br />\n<br />\n唔好打擊唔好分化咁簡單既事都做唔到？"},{"pid":"dc94a94b1c93657116226802c27e375f3602a8cc","tid":1277474,"uid":28878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:09:49.000Z","msg":"快起底"},{"pid":"247f4f8baafec1a7bc172761754d85e2e0f73659","tid":1277474,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:15:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee722726f9da0280e2da79b4c845fa8e4023252e","tid":1277474,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:15:55.000Z","msg":"再推<br />\n好撚柒嬲"},{"pid":"7d621e04fcfb6f6c112be84de38e17a5dbc5a7a9","tid":1277474,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:19:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad156dcafbd2c0e261479ff35760f0622d685e32","tid":1277474,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:25:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b66930a2750e453419cd0730af5d5a1bff22f4bd","tid":1277474,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:07:58.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n搵人幫手問"},{"pid":"4274579df62e0bdd0b04c020e4954443f0d5cc6e","tid":1277474,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T16:10:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"688dd9daec4bb9a8ccfa5e17ee0e97d05915fbc2","tid":1277474,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r